OL,3,CFarmer took his own life 'to save
OL,4,Cfarm' from inheritance tax, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA farmer took his own life the day
OL,8,Fbefore the Budget after weeks of
OL,9,Fworrying about looming changes to
OL,10,Finheritance tax, an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FJohn Charlesworth's son said he
OL,13,Fbelieved his father wanted to "beat"
OL,14,Fthe Government's proposals and "save
OL,15,Fthe farm for future generations".
OL,17,FMr Charlesworth, 78, who went by his
OL,18,Fmiddle name Philip, was found dead by
OL,19,Fhis son Jonathan Charlesworth, 47, in
OL,20,Fa barn of their farm in Silkstone,
OL,21,FBarnsley, on October 29 last year.
