OL,3,CFarmer took his own life 'to save
OL,4,Cfarm' from inheritance tax, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAn inquest at Sheffield Coroner's
OL,8,FCourt heard that Mr Charlesworth had
OL,9,Fbeen struggling to care for his wife,
OL,10,Fwho had severe dementia and had
OL,11,Frecently been diagnosed with cancer.
OL,13,FThe hearing was told that in the
OL,14,Fmonths before Rachel Reeves' Budget he
OL,15,Fhad been "growing more and more
OL,16,Fanxious about inheritance tax and the
OL,17,Fimplications for the farm".
OL,26,@wD@JOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
