OL,3,CFarmer took his own life 'to save
OL,4,Cfarm' from inheritance tax, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"There was a lack of information, it
OL,8,Fwasn't actually as bad as it could
OL,9,Fhave been but we didn't know that.
OL,11,F"We couldn't find any information, we
OL,12,Fjust knew it was coming, we didn't
OL,13,Fknow how bad it was going to be.
OL,15,F"I think he woke up that morning and
OL,16,Fthought, 'I'm not risking it, I'm not
OL,17,Frisking losing everything I've worked
OL,18,Ffor'."
