OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe added: "In the couple of months
OL,8,Fbefore it happened the only thing he
OL,9,Ftalked about was inheritance tax.
OL,11,F"I think he just wasn't going to let
OL,12,Fthe Government beat him, that was his
OL,13,Ffinal hurrah."
OL,15,FThe inquest heard that John
OL,16,FCharlesworth had retired from the
OL,17,Ffarm, which had been bought by his own
OL,18,Ffather, and that his son was
OL,19,Fresponsible for the day-to-day running
OL,20,Fwhile he cared for his wife, who died
OL,21,Fin February this year.
