OL,7,FA coroner was told he had no reported
OL,8,Fmental health issues, but had been
OL,9,Fseen by a mental health team about
OL,10,Fsupport for his wife several days
OL,11,Fbefore he died.
OL,13,FHis daughter Verity Charlesworth, 45,
OL,14,Fsaid farming was a part of Mr
OL,15,FCharlesworth's "life and identity",
OL,16,Fand that he was also a grandfather of
OL,17,Fsix and a keen bell-ringer.
