OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FRecording a conclusion of suicide,
OL,8,Fcoroner Tanyka Rawden said Mr
OL,9,FCharlesworth was under stress with
OL,10,Fcaring responsibilities for his wife.
OL,12,FShe said: "He was worried about
OL,13,Fimplications of new regulations around
OL,14,Finheritance tax that would see the
OL,15,Ffamily lose 50% of the farm, taking
OL,16,Fhis life the day before the changes
OL,17,Fwere due to be announced."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
