OL,7,FAfter the inquest, Jonathan
OL,8,FCharlesworth said his father was "a
OL,9,Ftypical Yorkshireman, typical farmer `
OL,10,Ftight with money but generous with
OL,11,Ftime", adding: "He'd do anything for
OL,12,Fanybody."
